{"tha-ap539:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap539:0.2":"Kaccayanavagga ","tha-ap539:0.3":"7 Mahakotthikattheraapadana ","tha-ap539:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap539:1.2":"sabbalokavidu muni; ","tha-ap539:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap539:1.4":"kappe uppajji cakkhuma. ","tha-ap539:2.1":"Ovadako vinnapako, ","tha-ap539:2.2":"tarako sabbapaninam; ","tha-ap539:2.3":"Desanakusalo buddho, ","tha-ap539:2.4":"taresi janatam bahum. ","tha-ap539:3.1":"Anukampako karuniko, ","tha-ap539:3.2":"hitesi sabbapaninam; ","tha-ap539:3.3":"Sampatte titthiye sabbe, ","tha-ap539:3.4":"pancasile patitthapi. ","tha-ap539:4.1":"Evam nirakulam asi, ","tha-ap539:4.2":"sunnatam titthiyehi ca; ","tha-ap539:4.3":"Vicittam arahantehi, ","tha-ap539:4.4":"vasibhutehi tadibhi. ","tha-ap539:5.1":"Ratananatthapannasam, ","tha-ap539:5.2":"uggato so mahamuni; ","tha-ap539:5.3":"Kancanagghiyasankaso, ","tha-ap539:5.4":"battimsavaralakkhano. ","tha-ap539:6.1":"Vassasatasahassani, ","tha-ap539:6.2":"ayu vijjati tavade; ","tha-ap539:6.3":"Tavata titthamano so, ","tha-ap539:6.4":"taresi janatam bahum. ","tha-ap539:7.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","tha-ap539:7.2":"brahmano vedaparagu; ","tha-ap539:7.3":"Upecca sabbalokaggam, ","tha-ap539:7.4":"assosim dhammadesanam. ","tha-ap539:8.1":"Tada so savakam viro, ","tha-ap539:8.2":"pabhinnamatigocaram; ","tha-ap539:8.3":"Atthe dhamme nirutte ca, ","tha-ap539:8.4":"patibhane ca kovidam. ","tha-ap539:9.1":"Thapesi etadaggamhi, ","tha-ap539:9.2":"tam sutva mudito aham; ","tha-ap539:9.3":"Sasavakam jinavaram, ","tha-ap539:9.4":"sattaham bhojayim tada. ","tha-ap539:10.1":"Dussehacchadayitvana, ","tha-ap539:10.2":"sasissam buddhisagaram; ","tha-ap539:10.3":"Nipacca padamulamhi, ","tha-ap539:10.4":"tam thanam patthayim aham. ","tha-ap539:11.1":"Tato avoca lokaggo, ","tha-ap539:11.2":"‘passathetam dijuttamam; ","tha-ap539:11.3":"Vinatam padamule me, ","tha-ap539:11.4":"kamalodarasappabham. ","tha-ap539:12.1":"Buddhasetthassa bhikkhussa, ","tha-ap539:12.2":"Thanam patthayate ayam; ","tha-ap539:12.3":"Taya saddhaya cagena, ","tha-ap539:12.4":"Saddhammassavanena ca. ","tha-ap539:13.1":"Sabbattha sukhito hutva, ","tha-ap539:13.2":"samsaritva bhavabhave; ","tha-ap539:13.3":"Anagatamhi addhane, ","tha-ap539:13.4":"lacchase tam manoratham. ","tha-ap539:14.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap539:14.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap539:14.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap539:14.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap539:15.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap539:15.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap539:15.3":"Kotthiko nama namena, ","tha-ap539:15.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap539:16.1":"Tam sutva mudito hutva, ","tha-ap539:16.2":"yavajivam tada jinam; ","tha-ap539:16.3":"Mettacitto paricarim, ","tha-ap539:16.4":"sato pannasamahito. ","tha-ap539:17.1":"Tena kammavipakena, ","tha-ap539:17.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap539:17.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap539:17.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap539:18.1":"Satanam tinikkhattunca, ","tha-ap539:18.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap539:18.3":"Satanam pancakkhattunca, ","tha-ap539:18.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap539:19.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap539:19.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap539:19.3":"Sabbattha sukhito asim, ","tha-ap539:19.4":"tassa kammassa vahasa. ","tha-ap539:20.1":"Duve bhave samsarami, ","tha-ap539:20.2":"devatte atha manuse; ","tha-ap539:20.3":"Annam gatim na gacchami, ","tha-ap539:20.4":"sucinnassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap539:21.1":"Duve kule pajayami, ","tha-ap539:21.2":"khattiye atha brahmane; ","tha-ap539:21.3":"Nice kule na jayami, ","tha-ap539:21.4":"sucinnassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap539:22.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","tha-ap539:22.2":"brahmabandhu ahosaham; ","tha-ap539:22.3":"Savatthiyam vippakule, ","tha-ap539:22.4":"paccajato mahaddhane. ","tha-ap539:23.1":"Mata candavati nama, ","tha-ap539:23.2":"pita me assalayano; ","tha-ap539:23.3":"Yada me pitaram buddho, ","tha-ap539:23.4":"vinayi sabbasuddhiya. ","tha-ap539:24.1":"Tada pasanno sugate, ","tha-ap539:24.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap539:24.3":"Moggallano acariyo, ","tha-ap539:24.4":"upajjha sarisambhavo. ","tha-ap539:25.1":"Kesesu chijjamanesu, ","tha-ap539:25.2":"ditthi chinna samulika; ","tha-ap539:25.3":"Nivasento ca kasavam, ","tha-ap539:25.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap539:26.1":"Atthadhammaniruttisu, ","tha-ap539:26.2":"patibhane ca me mati; ","tha-ap539:26.3":"Pabhinna tena lokaggo, ","tha-ap539:26.4":"etadagge thapesi mam. ","tha-ap539:27.1":"Asandittham viyakasim, ","tha-ap539:27.2":"upatissena pucchito; ","tha-ap539:27.3":"Patisambhidasu tenaham, ","tha-ap539:27.4":"aggo sambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap539:28.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap539:28.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap539:28.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap539:29.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap539:29.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap539:29.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap539:30.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap539:30.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap539:30.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap539:31.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma mahakotthiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap539:32.1":"Mahakotthikattherassapadanam sattamam. "}